わせ内容\" rows=\"10\"></textarea></td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n      <div class=\"img-c\">\n        <input type=\"submit\" value=\"　 確認 　\" />\n        \n        <input type=\"reset\" value=\"リセット\" />\n      </div>\n</form>\n</div>\n<div id=\"footer\">\n  <div class=\"area\">\n\t<div class=\"footer-info\">\n    <img src=\"images/footer-logo.jpg\" width=\"410\" height=\"58\" alt=\"INOKOZA　豚座建設株式会社\" /><br />\n    <p>\n      住所：〒787-0010 高知県四万十市古津賀2丁目6番地<br />\n      TEL：0880-34-6031<br />\n      FAX：0880-34-2850</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"page-top\"><a href=\"#header\"><img src=\"images/pagetop.jpg\" width=\"180\" height=\"34\" alt=\"ページの先頭へ戻る\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cr\">Copyright &copy; 豚座建設株式会社 All Rights Reserved.</div></div>\n</body>\n</html>","finalUrl":"https://www.inokoza.com/inquiry.html","rendered":false,"_cachedAt":"2026-06-23T22:07:24.612Z"}